com.easydataservices.ezsystem.java.exec

Class AppExec

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.easydataservices.ezsystem.java.exec.AppExec

  • public class AppExec
extends java.lang.Object
    An AppExec instance executes module routines. Methods in this class require the names of database objects (variables and routines) to be specified in camel case form. For example, an object in the database called CUSTOMER_ID must be specified using customerId.
    Version:
    2022.08.07
    Author:
    Jeremy Rickard
